Interface Summary

Class Summary
AbstractSampleQueueManager This class manages input, output and pending queues for samples that need to be evaluated or have been evaluated.
BasicSampleEvaluator This is class is an partial implementation of the interface SampleEvaluator.
BasicSampleQueueManager This class implements a simple first-in-first-out queue
BatchSampleEvaluator Same as BasicSampleEvaluator, only now samples can be evaluated in batches
DefaultSampleEvaluator A helper class for implementing SampleEvaluator
DefaultSampleQueueManager  
EvaluationUnit An evaluation unit encapsulate a sample point for evaluation.
EvaluationUnitBatch  
ExternalSimulator  
LocalSampleEvaluator This class implements a local sample evaluator.
PrioritySampleQueueManager This class implements a priority FIFO queue, points with the highest priority are fetched first
